title: FULLY EQUIPPED 2 BEDROOM! CUSTOM LIST AVAILABLE!
posting_body: ['LISTING ID 6383561', 'This apartment located in a rental community in Pompano Beach features one, two and three bedroom floor plans,', 'a fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, a dishwasher, wood flooring, a living room and a dining room.', 'Enjoy the comforts of central A/C, in-unit laundry and off-street parking.', 'The community offers a clubhouse with a business center, a resident lounge, pool with a sundeck and a fitness center.', 'This community is also deleaded and pet friendly.', 'Located within a five minute drive to the I-95.', 'LISTING ID 6383561', '*PLEASE REFERENCE ABOVE LISTING ID', 'WHEN INQUIRING*', 'Stop searching.', 'You’ve already come to the right place.', 'If you’re looking for ANY type of property whether it’s a studio, an apartment, a townhouse or single family home...', 'YES WE GOT IT.', 'We’re a ONE STOP shop that can assist you in taking the next step towards your next home today.', 'No one makes it this easy!', 'Just send us a text to', 'show contact info', 'with your name and we can send you a CUSTOM list of properties that match what you’re looking for and get the process started.', 'Thank you!', '*DISCLAIMER - We do post properties for a 30 day period of time.', 'Due to High Rental Demand, some properties advertised may be withdrawn, cancelled, rented, pending or sold within the past 30 days.', 'All information is deemed to be correct, but not guaranteed*']
